&lt;li&gt;Dynamic, enthusiastic, tenacious, team-oriented mindset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working within a quota and commission structure&lt;/li&gt;
